The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-08-2014 TUES...PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET




        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 4/8/14Tuesday, April 08, 2014 


Glenn covers the latest updates regarding former Mozilla CEO Brendan Eich,

 speaks with Tim Ballard about a mission to save children 
          from being sex slaves and is joined by Ralph Reed
              to talk about his new book, 
                "Awakening, How America Can Turn From 
                    Economic and Moral Destruction Back to Greatness,"
                         and how to save America. 

            That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
